"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?18/44/19140/abstract/2\">",
"      Trinder J, Whitworth F, Kay A, Wilkin P. Respiratory instability during sleep onset. J Appl Physiol 1992; 73:2462.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?18/44/19140/abstract/3\">",
"      Badr MS, Skatrud JB, Dempsey JA. Determinants of poststimulus potentiation in humans during NREM sleep. J Appl Physiol 1992; 73:1958.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?18/44/19140/abstract/4\">",
"      Badr MS, Morgan BJ, Finn L, et al. Ventilatory response to induced auditory arousals during NREM sleep. Sleep 1997; 20:707.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?18/44/19140/abstract/5\">",
"      Berssenbrugge A, Dempsey J, Iber C, et al. Mechanisms of hypoxia-induced periodic breathing during sleep in humans. J Physiol 1983; 343:507.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?18/44/19140/abstract/6\">",
"      Leevers AM, Simon PM, Dempsey JA. Apnea after normocapnic mechanical ventilation during NREM sleep. J Appl Physiol 1994; 77:2079.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?18/44/19140/abstract/7\">",
"      Khoo MC, Kronauer RE, Strohl KP, Slutsky AS. Factors inducing periodic breathing in humans: a general model. J Appl Physiol 1982; 53:644.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?18/44/19140/abstract/8\">",
"      Khoo MC. Determinants of ventilatory instability and variability. Respir Physiol 2000; 122:167.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
